{"doc":{"isTranslated":false,"flaws":{},"title":"padding","mdn_url":"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/padding","locale":"en-US","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS\">CSS</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Reference\">CSS Reference</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Box_Model\">CSS Box Model</a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Guides</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Box_Model/Introduction_to_the_CSS_box_model\">Introduction to the CSS basic box model</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Box_Model/Mastering_margin_collapsing\">Mastering margin collapsing</a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Properties</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/height\"><code>height</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/margin-bottom\"><code>margin-bottom</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/margin-left\"><code>margin-left</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/margin-right\"><code>margin-right</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/margin-top\"><code>margin-top</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon experimental\" viewBox=\"0 0 100 100\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" role=\"img\">\n    <title>This is an experimental API that should not be used in production code.</title>\n    <path d=\"M90.72 82.34c4.4 7 1.29 12.66-7 12.66H16.25C8 95 4.88 89.31 9.28 82.34l29.47-46.46V12.5H35A3.75 3.75 0 0135 5h30a3.75 3.75 0 010 7.5h-3.75v23.38zM45.08 39.86L29.14 65h41.72L54.92 39.86l-1.17-1.81V12.5h-7.5v25.55z\"></path>\n</svg><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/margin-trim\"><code>margin-trim</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/margin\"><code>margin</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/max-height\"><code>max-height</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/max-width\"><code>max-width</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/min-height\"><code>min-height</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/min-width\"><code>min-width</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/overscroll-behavior-block\"><code>overscroll-behavior-block</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/overscroll-behavior-inline\"><code>overscroll-behavior-inline</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/overscroll-behavior-x\"><code>overscroll-behavior-x</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/overscroll-behavior-y\"><code>overscroll-behavior-y</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/overscroll-behavior\"><code>overscroll-behavior</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/padding-bottom\"><code>padding-bottom</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/padding-left\"><code>padding-left</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/padding-right\"><code>padding-right</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/padding-top\"><code>padding-top</code></a></li><li><em><code>padding</code></em></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/visibility\"><code>visibility</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/width\"><code>width</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div></div>\n\n<p>The <strong><code>padding</code></strong> <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS\">CSS</a> <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Shorthand_properties\">shorthand property</a> sets the <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Box_Model/Introduction_to_the_CSS_box_model#padding-area\">padding area</a> on all four sides of an element at once.</p>\n\n<div><iframe class=\"interactive\" width=\"100%\" height=\"250\" src=\"https://interactive-examples.mdn.mozilla.net/pages/css/padding.html\" title=\"MDN Web Docs Interactive Example\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe>\n\n<p class=\"hidden\">The source for this interactive example is stored in a GitHub repository. If you'd like to contribute to the interactive examples project, please clone <a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/interactive-examples\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">https://github.com/mdn/interactive-examples</a> and send us a pull request.</p></div>\n\n\n\n<p>An element's padding area is the space between its content and its border.</p>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\">\n<p><strong>Note:</strong> Padding creates extra space within an element. In contrast, <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/margin\"><code>margin</code></a> creates extra space <em>around</em> an element.</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"Constituent_properties","title":"Constituent properties","isH3":false,"content":"<p>This property is a shorthand for the following CSS properties:</p>\n\n<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/padding-bottom\"><code>padding-bottom</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/padding-left\"><code>padding-left</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/padding-right\"><code>padding-right</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/padding-top\"><code>padding-top</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"Syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"brush:css no-line-numbers notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token comment\">/* Apply to all four sides */</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">padding</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 1em<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">/* vertical | horizontal */</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">padding</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 5% 10%<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">/* top | horizontal | bottom */</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">padding</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 1em 2em 2em<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">/* top | right | bottom | left */</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">padding</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 5px 1em 0 2em<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">/* Global values */</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">padding</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> inherit<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">padding</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> initial<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">padding</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> unset<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>The <code>padding</code> property may be specified using one, two, three, or four values. Each value is a <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/length\"><code>&lt;length&gt;</code></a> or a <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/percentage\"><code>&lt;percentage&gt;</code></a>. Negative values are invalid.</p>\n\n<ul>\n <li>When <strong>one</strong> value is specified, it applies the same padding to <strong>all four sides</strong>.</li>\n <li>When <strong>two</strong> values are specified, the first padding applies to the <strong>top and bottom</strong>, the second to the <strong>left and right</strong>.</li>\n <li>When <strong>three</strong> values are specified, the first padding applies to the <strong>top</strong>, the second to the <strong>right and left</strong>, the third to the <strong>bottom</strong>.</li>\n <li>When <strong>four</strong> values are specified, the paddings apply to the <strong>top</strong>, <strong>right</strong>, <strong>bottom</strong>, and <strong>left</strong> in that order (clockwise).</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"Values","title":"Values","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/length\"><code>&lt;length&gt;</code></a></dt>\n <dd>The size of the padding as a fixed value.</dd>\n <dt><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/percentage\"><code>&lt;percentage&gt;</code></a></dt>\n <dd>The size of the padding as a percentage, relative to the <em>width</em> of the containing block.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"Formal_definition","title":"Formal definition","isH3":false,"content":"<p><table class=\"properties\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"row\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/initial_value\">Initial value</a></th><td>as each of the properties of the shorthand:<br><ul><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/padding-bottom\"><code>padding-bottom</code></a>: <code>0</code></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/padding-left\"><code>padding-left</code></a>: <code>0</code></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/padding-right\"><code>padding-right</code></a>: <code>0</code></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/padding-top\"><code>padding-top</code></a>: <code>0</code></li></ul></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Applies to</th><td>all elements, except <code>table-row-group</code>, <code>table-header-group</code>, <code>table-footer-group</code>, <code>table-row</code>, <code>table-column-group</code> and <code>table-column</code>. It also applies to <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/::first-letter\"><code>::first-letter</code></a> and <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/::first-line\"><code>::first-line</code></a>.</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/inheritance\">Inherited</a></th><td>no</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Percentages</th><td>refer to the width of the containing block</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/computed_value\">Computed value</a></th><td>as each of the properties of the shorthand:<br><ul><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/padding-bottom\"><code>padding-bottom</code></a>: the percentage as specified or the absolute length</li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/padding-left\"><code>padding-left</code></a>: the percentage as specified or the absolute length</li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/padding-right\"><code>padding-right</code></a>: the percentage as specified or the absolute length</li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/padding-top\"><code>padding-top</code></a>: the percentage as specified or the absolute length</li></ul></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Animation type</th><td>a <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/length#interpolation\" title=\"Values of the <length> CSS data type are interpolated as real, floating-point numbers.\">length</a></td></tr></tbody></table></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"Formal_syntax","title":"Formal syntax","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"brush: css notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token selector\">[ &lt;length&gt; | &lt;percentage&gt; ]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>1<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>4<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"Examples","title":"Examples","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"Setting_padding_with_pixels","title":"Setting padding with pixels","isH3":true,"content":"<h4 id=\"HTML\">HTML</h4>\n\n<pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>h4</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>This element has moderate padding.<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>h4</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>h3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>The padding is huge in this element!<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>h3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre>\n\n<h4 id=\"CSS\">CSS</h4>\n\n<pre class=\"brush: css notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token selector\">h4</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">background-color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> lime<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">padding</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 20px 50px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token selector\">h3</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">background-color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> cyan<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">padding</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 110px 50px 50px 110px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre>\n\n<h4 id=\"Result\">Result</h4>\n\n<p><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" id=\"frame_Setting_padding_with_pixels\" width=\"100%\" height=\"300\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/padding/_samples_/Setting_padding_with_pixels\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"Setting_padding_with_pixels_and_percentages","title":"Setting padding with pixels and percentages","isH3":true,"content":"<pre class=\"brush: css notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token property\">padding</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 5%<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>                <span class=\"token comment\">/* All sides: 5% padding */</span>\n\n<span class=\"token property\">padding</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 10px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>              <span class=\"token comment\">/* All sides: 10px padding */</span>\n\n<span class=\"token property\">padding</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 10px 20px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>         <span class=\"token comment\">/* top and bottom: 10px padding */</span>\n                            <span class=\"token comment\">/* left and right: 20px padding */</span>\n\n<span class=\"token property\">padding</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 10px 3% 20px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>      <span class=\"token comment\">/* top:            10px padding */</span>\n                            <span class=\"token comment\">/* left and right: 3% padding   */</span>\n                            <span class=\"token comment\">/* bottom:         20px padding */</span>\n\n<span class=\"token property\">padding</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 1em 3px 30px 5px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>  <span class=\"token comment\">/* top:    1em padding  */</span>\n                            <span class=\"token comment\">/* right:  3px padding  */</span>\n                            <span class=\"token comment\">/* bottom: 30px padding */</span>\n                            <span class=\"token comment\">/* left:   5px padding  */</span> </code></pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"Specifications","title":"Specifications","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specification</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comment</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-box-3/#padding-shorthand\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">CSS Basic Box Model<br><small lang=\"en-US\">The definition of 'padding' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-cr\">Candidate Recommendation</span></td>\n   <td>No change.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/CSS2/box.html#propdef-padding\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">CSS Level&nbsp;2 (Revision&nbsp;1)<br><small lang=\"en-US\">The definition of 'padding' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Recommendation</span></td>\n   <td>No change.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/CSS1/#padding\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">CSS Level&nbsp;1<br><small lang=\"en-US\">The definition of 'padding' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Recommendation</span></td>\n   <td>Initial definition.</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browser compatibility","id":"Browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"css.properties.padding","dataURL":"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/padding/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"See_also","title":"See also","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Box_Model/Introduction_to_the_CSS_box_model\">Introduction to the CSS basic box model</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/padding-top\"><code>padding-top</code></a>, <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/padding-right\"><code>padding-right</code></a>, <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/padding-bottom\"><code>padding-bottom</code></a>, and <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/padding-left\"><code>padding-left</code></a>.</li>\n <li>The mapped logical properties: <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/padding-block-start\"><code>padding-block-start</code></a>, <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/padding-block-end\"><code>padding-block-end</code></a>, <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/padding-inline-start\"><code>padding-inline-start</code></a>, and <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/padding-inline-end\"><code>padding-inline-end</code></a> and the shorthands <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/padding-block\"><code>padding-block</code></a> and <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/padding-inline\"><code>padding-inline</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Constituent properties","id":"Constituent_properties"},{"text":"Syntax","id":"Syntax"},{"text":"Formal definition","id":"Formal_definition"},{"text":"Formal syntax","id":"Formal_syntax"},{"text":"Examples","id":"Examples"},{"text":"Specifications","id":"Specifications"},{"text":"Browser compatibility","id":"Browser_compatibility"},{"text":"See also","id":"See_also"}],"summary":"The padding CSS shorthand property sets the padding area on all four sides of an element at once.","popularity":0.0864,"modified":"2021-02-19T18:56:36.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"padding","url":"/ca/docs/Web/CSS/padding","locale":"ca"},{"title":"padding","url":"/de/docs/Web/CSS/padding","locale":"de"},{"title":"padding","url":"/es/docs/Web/CSS/padding","locale":"es"},{"title":"padding","url":"/fr/docs/Web/CSS/padding","locale":"fr"},{"title":"padding","url":"/ja/docs/Web/CSS/padding","locale":"ja"},{"title":"padding","url":"/ko/docs/Web/CSS/padding","locale":"ko"},{"title":"padding","url":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/CSS/padding","locale":"pt-BR"},{"title":"padding","url":"/ru/docs/Web/CSS/padding","locale":"ru"},{"title":"padding","url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/padding","locale":"zh-CN"}],"source":{"folder":"en-us/web/css/padding","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/blob/main/files/en-us/web/css/padding/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/commit/2a14c0eac061493b1160076a3e72ec8e346d2223"},"parents":[{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web","title":"Web technology for developers"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS","title":"CSS: Cascading Style Sheets"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/padding","title":"padding"}],"pageTitle":"padding - CSS: Cascading Style Sheets | MDN","noIndexing":false}}